Day 77: Jenkins Deploy Pipeline

Date: November 30, 2025
Overview
Created my first deployment pipeline using Jenkinsfile.
Key Concepts Learned

Declarative pipeline syntax
Pipeline stages
Agent configuration
Pipeline as code

Jenkinsfile
groovypipeline {
    agent any
    stages {
        stage('Build') {
            steps {
                sh 'npm install'
                sh 'npm run build'
            }
        }
        stage('Test') {
            steps {
                sh 'npm test'
            }
        }
        stage('Deploy') {
            steps {
                sh 'scp -r build/* user@server:/var/www/html/'
            }
        }
    }
}

Challenges Faced
Pipeline syntax errors! One wrong bracket breaks the entire pipeline.
